199
00:17:15,045 --> 00:17:20,970
And it looks like that was done in conjunction or like in collaboration with the health department.

200
00:17:21,871 --> 00:17:23,472
And I'm not sure if we

201
00:17:25,298 --> 00:17:26,818
I'm not sure how that process works.

202
00:17:26,858 --> 00:17:35,781
If we want to collaborate with the health department again, or if they have something already about service animals.

203
00:17:36,221 --> 00:17:42,543
