204
00:17:42,623 --> 00:17:46,284
Service animals are not the same as emotional support cats.

205
00:17:46,384 --> 00:17:49,445
So I want to make sure that that's very, very

206
00:17:50,513 --> 00:17:53,494
clear to people, there's a clear distinction.

207
00:17:53,514 --> 00:18:03,696
And that is why emotional support pets don't necessarily fall under ADA reasonable accommodations and things of that nature.

208
00:18:04,156 --> 00:18:13,459
So if we were going to do that, and I'm sure that the Board of Health probably did it as well, but I think that that's something that can be updated later on.

209
00:18:13,499 --> 00:18:18,700
