215
00:18:48,306 --> 00:19:08,190
I think for our state in particular, the emotional support animals, the regs are slightly more giving than

216
00:19:16,813 --> 00:19:18,474
the federal regs.

217
00:19:21,235 --> 00:19:28,459
For service animals, the federal regs are it.

218
00:19:34,102 --> 00:19:35,223
The be all and end all.

219
00:19:42,920 --> 00:20:00,160
